            </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <row>
               <entry>ram</entry>
               <entry>The amount of memory to be allocated for a virtual machine server in kilobytes, megabytes, or 
              gigabytes specified as nX where:
              <variablelist>
                     <varlistentry>
                        <term>
                           <emphasis>n</emphasis>
                        </term>
                        <listitem>
                           <para>is an integer greater than zero</para>
                        </listitem>
                     </varlistentry>
                     <varlistentry>
                        <term>X</term>
                        <listitem>
                           <para>is one of "K", "M" or "G"</para>
                        </listitem>
                     </varlistentry>
                  </variablelist>            
               </entry>
            </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
